ct. While the system currently indicates \"need 0 more,\" the \"critically low\" status overrides this and demands action.\n    *   **Recommendation:** Initiate an urgent reorder for the iphone17 pro max. Determine an appropriate reorder quantity based on historical sales data (if available prior to this period) or projected demand to prevent future stock",
